data.description: Fall move-in! Introducing the Bellamy at newly opened Ashford Place in Plainfield. This 2,051 sq ft, two-story, open concept home features 4 large bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a spacious study, 2 car garage, and a full basement. Oversized windows and 9-foot ceilings help to brighten up the home from within. Entering from the garage is a large drop zone area to hang up coats and kick-off shoes. From there, awaits the beautiful kitchen, featuring designer cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, Quartz countertops, and a large island overlooking the dining and great room. The second level contains 4 large bedrooms each with its own closet, two full-sized baths, and a convenient upstairs laundry. The primary bedroom includes an impeccable bathroom with double bowl vanities, a large shower, a private water room, and a huge walk-in closet with enough room to share. Step inside to see all that D.R. Horton homes have to offer. Our homes are built with energy-efficient standards and include both Smart Home technology and a 1, 2, & 10-year Home Warranty. Convenient to shopping, restaurants, and more! Photos represent similar homes. Schedule an appointment today! All DR Horton Chicago homes include our America's Smart Home Technology which allows you to monitor and control your home from the comfort of your sofa or from 500 miles away and connects to your home with your smartphone, tablet or computer.
